# Project Documentation

This folder contains the complete project documentation for the **AI-Enabled Student Admission System**, developed using **Salesforce Developer Edition**.

## Project Overview

The **AI-Enabled Student Admission System** is a Salesforce-based solution designed to streamline and improve student admission management through centralized data management, workflow automation, AI-assisted guidance, reporting, dashboards, and role-based access control.

The system helps manage student information, courses, enrolments, admission-related processes, and communication within a unified Salesforce environment.

