## Project Objectives

The main objectives of the project are to:

- Centralize student admission information.
- Reduce manual admission processing.
- Automate repetitive administrative tasks.
- Improve data accuracy through validation rules.
- Support admission workflows using Salesforce automation.
- Provide AI-assisted guidance using Agentforce.
- Improve visibility through reports and dashboards.
- Implement secure role-based access to admission data.

## Project Workflow

1. Student information is created and managed in Salesforce.
2. Course information is maintained in the system.
3. Student enrolment records are created and tracked.
4. Validation rules ensure data accuracy.
5. Salesforce automation processes admission-related workflows.
6. Approval processes support controlled review where required.
7. Email templates and alerts automate communication.
8. Agentforce provides AI-assisted admission guidance.
9. Reports and dashboards provide operational insights.
10. Profiles, roles, and permission sets control system access.

